name: Aliens Invade! [EARLY ACCESS]
description:
Aliens Are ATTACKING? Now the human race is at risk!!! No Human is Powerful Enough to stop them, so who will? A traitor of the Alien Race. His Name is Bloopy. He knows all their plans, and he knows where to go. But It's One alien against Hundreds. Can Bloopy stop the evil aliens, or will he just fall down to them?

This Game is a Prototype of a future game I am willing to create. Just leave suggestions, and I will give them.
